WEBVTT

00:00:01.083 --> 00:00:03.809
On August 12, 2020,

00:00:03.833 --> 00:00:07.268
two groups of girls
went out to protest in Minsk,

00:00:07.292 --> 00:00:09.726
the capital city of Belarus.

00:00:09.750 --> 00:00:11.434
They put on white clothes

00:00:11.458 --> 00:00:14.000
and went barefoot out into the street.

00:00:14.833 --> 00:00:16.101
In the morning,

00:00:16.125 --> 00:00:19.601
some went to Komarovskiy Market
in the center of town.

00:00:19.625 --> 00:00:20.893
Later that day,

00:00:20.917 --> 00:00:23.226
the other group gathered with flowers

00:00:23.250 --> 00:00:26.809
at the eternal flame
under the victory monument.

00:00:26.833 --> 00:00:29.143
They stood together holding hands,

00:00:29.167 --> 00:00:32.476
and they started to sing
the Belarusian lullaby,